title: #134: Ill Mannered, Needy Robot Babies
description:
Ronnie Karam (TrashTalkTV) and Ben Mandelker (bsideblog) mull over a week full of bad manners and needy wives on Ladies of London, Married to Medicine, Real Housewives of Orange County and Real Housewives of New York. We also vomit (no, seriously) while discussing Cinnamon Girl diet shakes and chat a bit about Big Brother for those of you who requested it. Come on in!
